byline.contributor: Kareem Fahim contributed reporting from Bani Walid, Libya.

abstract: Secretary of State Hillary Rodham Clinton pledges political and economic support for Libya's transitional government; Clintion is highest-ranking American official to visit Libya since collapse of Col Muammar el-Qaddafi's government.
snippet: The secretary of state is the highest-ranking American official to visit Libya since the collapse of Colonel Qaddafi’s government two months ago.
